{"tid":1951306,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情停擺之前 英超高層計劃3月21日為利物浦頒獎","createTime":"2020-03-31T01:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T03:33:30.000Z","uid":173952,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f93a4267fd9f81b189135cb13b1ea3a3d981a3c","tid":1951306,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"3月31日訊 據《鏡報》消息，在疫情導致英超暫停之前，英超聯賽的高層曾有個「秘密計劃」。由於擔憂新冠疫情加重，高層嘗試提前為利物浦舉行頒獎典禮。<br />\n<br />\n  利物浦距離英超奪冠僅剩2場勝利，這將是球隊時隔30年再次捧起聯賽冠軍獎盃。按照原計劃，如果紅軍連續擊敗愛華頓和水晶宮，他們可以於3月21日的週六在晏菲路鎖定冠軍冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n  根據英超規定，利物浦若奪冠，要等到聯賽最後一個主場才能舉起獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n  儘管沒有達成正式的協議，但英超高層此前進行過討論，將英超獎盃提前帶到晏菲路，允許利物浦在主場球迷面前慶祝這一歷史性時刻。<br />\n<br />\n  但是由於新冠病毒肆虐導致英超停擺，利物浦最終沒能在3月21日接過英超獎盃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0daf9afbeed9b63cfb77e4e981dbceddafca52","tid":1951306,"uid":238920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"平常心"},{"pid":"d522d2bcc7c2b97ec7ce05db470de999fae02b80","tid":1951306,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2365b9d9bd2698df2c6b3899b722965963de4561","tid":1951306,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\